{
  "stem": "15694.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Janek. ?] He impressed me very much with his big bike, motorbike.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He took me in-- in a side car, and went in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it was very exciting, and at some-- at one point, I-- I swear I was about-- above a precipice when he took a curve, a bend.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And now at this particular point, he didn't change my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But I met him later in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was still winter 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He was buying gold and other valuables in Zakopane, and came to Krakow to sell it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now I have to switch back again in order for this story to make more sense.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "When the war started, all my relations disappeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And where my father stayed, he had a factory of cucumbers and jam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And another brother of my grandfather arrived and took over the whole stock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- my father and myself-- had our first lesson.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had my first lesson, anyway, in selling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't difficult because the black market already had started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in time of war, where everything is easily sold, you know, especially food stuffs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's my first experience in selling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, when that finished, that's about the time when this [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Janek ?] appeared with gold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I asked him if I should sell it for him, or rather my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we invited him to our flat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father sold what he had to sell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And was-- that was his first contact with the black market.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, the black market was something which turned out the only-- the only thing to be-- sort of to earn some money with, because everything else you start, we weren't very lucky.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
